videos.description: Jonah Mathews hits a 3-pointer over an Oregon defender to increase USC's lead to 62-58 after being down by as many as 11.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mathews hits tough 3 over Oregon defense) 2020/1/23

videos.headline: Mathews hits tough 3 over Oregon defense

videos.description: Payton Pritchard speeds down the lane to lay the ball in and tie the score at 62-62 with under 30 seconds left.

videos.headline: Pritchard's layup sends game to OT
